data.enText: a secret word or phrase that you need to know in order to be allowed into a place
a series of letters or numbers that you must type into a computer or computer system in order to be able to use it

data.chText: 进入系统请键入用户名称和密码。
data.enText: Enter a username and password to get into the system.

tr: a secret word or phrase known only to a restricted group

value.def: A password is a secret word or phrase that you must know in order to be allowed to enter a place such as a military base, or to be allowed to use a computer system.

example.ex: No-one could use the computer unless they had a password.
example.tran: 除非知道密码，否则谁也用不了那台计算机。
